description:
This is a 8 minute workout called 'Strengthen Your Core - Just 6 Minutes A Day!' from the channel Tone and Tighten.
The workout falls under Strength/Body weight and Cardio/Mat.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Foundation Builder and The Comfort Moves vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Strengthen your core in just 6 minutes a day with this simple, effective home workout! 9 great exercises to strengthen your complete core including your abs, obliques, lower back, and hips. Led by a physical therapist to help you increase core strength, decrease pain, and help you look and feel your best.
